"Four

per centum

of the amount by which the net gifts exceed fifty thousand pesos and do not exceed seventy thousand pesos;

"Five

per centum

of the amount by which the net gifts exceed seventy thousand pesos and do not exceed one hundred thousand pesos;

"Seven

per centum

of the amount by which the net gifts exceed one hundred thousand pesos and do not exceed one hundred and fifty thousand pesos;

"Nine

per centum

of the amount by which the net gifts exceed one hundred and fifty thousand pesos and do not exceed two hundred and fifty thousand pesos;

"Eleven

per centum

of the amount by which the net gifts exceed two hundred and fifty thousand pesos and do not exceed five hundred thousand pesos;

"Thirteen

per centum

of the amount by which the net gifts exceed five hundred thousand pesos and do not exceed one million pesos;

"Fifteen

per centum

of the amount by which the net gifts exceed one million pesos;

"The tax provided, in this section shall not apply in every case where the donor makes the gift in favor of an educational institution, foundation, trust and/or the Jose Rizal National Centennial Commission."
